    "description": "THIS IS NOT YOUR HOUSE:  A Psychological Horror Choose Your Own Adventure game with ten endings. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will take on the role of Roger; an elderly widower returning home from an afternoon of errands; only to discover his locks have been changed, and someone else is living in his house. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTake Your House Back, or let the intruder keep it and find another way to survive without your most basic need, SHELTER.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game is a Choose Your Own Adventure Visual Novel where you will make a series of branching choices which will lead to one of ten unique endings. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nOn repeat playthroughs you will have the option to Skip any part of the story you've already been through and be taken immediately to the next choice in the story. Making it more convenient to do multiple playthroughs and find all the endings.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPressing the &quot;V&quot; button in-game activates a Screen Reader which will tell you what button your cursor is hovering over, as well as reading in-game dialogue, narration, and choice buttons to you.",
